# 🏍️ C Bike Engine Simulator

A lightweight, high-performance C simulation of a motorcycle internal combustion engine.

## Features
- **Sequential Gearbox Logic**: Simulates a standard 1-N-2-3-4-5-6 shift pattern.
- **Thermodynamics**: Temperature increases based on RPM and throttle load.
- **RPM Simulation**: Realistic idle and redline limits.

## How to Build
```bash
make
./bike_sim
